p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-and-Britney-Spears.-CREDIT_-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-and-Steve-Granitz_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tate-mcrae">泰特·麦克雷（Tate McRae）</a>对她和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears">布兰妮·斯皮尔斯（Britney Spears）</a>之间的经常比较开放。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tate-mcrae-so-close-to-what-review-3840099">泰特·麦克莱</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位加拿大歌手（2月21日）发行了她的专辑《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tate-mcrae-so-close-to-what-review-3840099">如此接近的内容</a>》  - 近年来被比作1990年代和2000年代的流行歌星，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christina-aguilera">克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉（Christina Aguilera）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pussycat-dolls">猫咪娃娃（Pussycat Dolls）</a>等艺术家。</p><p>但是，最常见的是长矛，粉丝注意到两位艺术家的声乐风格和编舞中的相似之处。现在，在对《 <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/tate-mcrae-lyrics-album-kid-laroi-b2702379.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>独立报》</em></a>的新采访中，麦克雷分享了她与“有毒”歌手相比的想法。</p><p> “我觉得那个讨人喜欢和恐怖。这真是一个疯狂的声明，因为没有人可以与布兰妮·斯皮尔斯（Britney Spears）相提并论。就像将某人与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>进行比较！”她告诉出版物。 “那是蓝图！” </p><figure id="attachment_3840253" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3840253" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3840253" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025.jpg" alt="泰特·麦克雷（Tate McRae）“如此接近什么”促销。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Tate-McRae-promo-photo-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3840253" class="wp-caption-text">泰特·麦克雷（Tate McRae）“如此接近”促销活动。</figcaption></figure><p> <em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tate-mcrae-so-close-to-what-review-3840099">四星级评论“如此接近什么”的评论</a>中指出，麦克雷的制作人（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/onerepublic">Onerepublic的</a>主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-tedder">瑞安·特德（Ryan Tedder）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">凯莉·米洛格（Kylie Minogue）</a>合作者Lostboy）“联想起新鲜的，俱乐部的俱乐部，俱乐部，俱乐部准备好跳动，点头，向Flip Phone Phone Era的光泽地板填充者致敬” 。</p><p>它继续说：“再次&#39;小姐的所有格&#39;，回想起<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ciara">ciara</a>和pussycat娃娃（再次），而&#39;我知道爱情&